No. 10-11207. Michelle Miller, aka Michelle Favreau, aka Michelle Brodeau, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 933, 132 S. Ct. 379,

181 L. Ed. 2d 239,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6572. October 3, 2011.
